title: KSI Needs To Stop The Cringy Apologies...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! KSI recently said something that probably should have been left on the cutting room floor. I'm always one to see a good apology video but to see it so overdone like this is just hilarious. Thanks for watching!
